<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Happy Birthday 🎂</title>

<style>
body{
  margin:0;
  font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
  background:#ffe4ec;
  text-align:center;
  overflow:hidden;
}

.slide{
  display:none;
  padding:60px 20px;
}

.active{
  display:block;
  animation:fade 0.8s ease;
}

@keyframes fade{
  from{opacity:0;}
  to{opacity:1;}
}

h1{font-size:55px; color:#8b0033;}
h2{font-size:40px;}
p{font-size:24px; max-width:700px; margin:auto;}

button{
  padding:14px 25px;
  font-size:18px;
  border:none;
  border-radius:25px;
  margin:10px;
  cursor:pointer;
}

.next{background:#ff4d6d; color:white;}
.exit{background:#b3003c; color:white;}

img{
  width:250px;
  margin:20px;
  border-radius:20px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<audio id="music" loop>
  <source src="hotline.mp3">
</audio>

<!-- 1 OPENING -->
<div class="slide active">
  <h1>hey birthday girl 🎂</h1>
  <p>
  i made something for you…  
  don’t overthink it, just go through it okay?
  </p>
  <img src="bunny1.jpg">
  <br>
  <button class="next" onclick="nextSlide()">start</button>
</div>

<!-- 2 MORNING -->
<div class="slide">
  <h2>good morning 🐰</h2>
  <p>
  pompom’s been with you right?  
  i hope she’s taking care of you for me
  </p>
  <img src="pompom.jpg">
  <br>
  <button class="next" onclick="nextSlide()">continue</button>
</div>

<!-- 3 FLOWERS -->
<div class="slide">
  <h2>i got you flowers 🌸</h2>
  <p>
  rose lilies and tulips…  
  see? i actually pay attention sometimes
  </p>
  <img src="flowers.jpg">
  <br>
  <button onclick="sendEmail()">receive bouquet 💌</button>
  <button class="next" onclick="nextSlide()">next</button>
</div>

<!-- 4 FOOD -->
<div class="slide">
  <h2>eat first</h2>
  <p>
  don’t say you’re not hungry…  
  i already know how you are 😐
  </p>
  <img src="cake.jpg">
  <br>
  <button class="next" onclick="nextSlide()">ok fine</button>
</div>

<!-- 5 SINGING -->
<div class="slide">
  <h2>okay don’t laugh 💀</h2>
  <p>
  i actually tried here…  
  so be nice for like 2 minutes
  </p>

  <!-- AUDIO -->
  <audio controls>
    <source src="sing.mp3">
  </audio>

  <!-- OR VIDEO -->
  <!--
  <video width="300" controls>
    <source src="sing.mp4">
  </video>
  -->

  <br>
  <button class="next" onclick="nextSlide()">be honest</button>
</div>

<!-- 6 BUNNY BREAK -->
<div class="slide">
  <h2>important break 🐰</h2>
  <p>
  i still think pompom was a good choice…  
  she kinda matches you
  </p>
  <img src="bunny2.jpg">
  <br>
  <button class="next" onclick="nextSlide()">continue</button>
</div>

<!-- 7 EXTRA EMOTIONAL -->
<div class="slide">
  <h2>random thought</h2>
  <p>
  i like knowing something i gave you  
  is there with you today
  </p>
  <br>
  <button class="next" onclick="nextSlide()">next</button>
</div>

<!-- 8 SHIFT -->
<div class="slide">
  <h2>okay… for real</h2>
  <p>
  i wish i was actually there with you today…  
  not just doing this through a screen
  </p>
  <br>
  <button onclick="finalSlide()">next</button>
</div>

<!-- FINAL -->
<div class="slide">
  <h2>happy birthday ❤️</h2>
  <p>
  i know this isn’t the same as being there with you,  
  but i still wanted to make something that’s actually yours.  

  not just something random… but something that reminds you  
  that someone out there is thinking about you today.  

  you’re not nonchalant like you act sometimes,  
  you care more than you show,  
  and i notice that.  

  i like how you balance things…  
  how you can be sarcastic one second  
  and soft the next without even trying.  

  and yeah, i don’t always say things directly,  
  but i hope you can feel it through this.  

  i’m really glad it’s you.  

  enjoy your day, okay?  

  – lloyd
  </p>
</div>

<script>
let slides=document.querySelectorAll(".slide");
let current=0;
let music=document.getElementById("music");
let started=false;

function startMusic(){
  if(!started){
    music.play();
    started=true;
  }
}

function nextSlide(){
  startMusic();
  slides[current].classList.remove("active");
  current++;
  slides[current].classList.add("active");
}

function finalSlide(){
  slides[current].classList.remove("active");
  current++;
  slides[current].classList.add("active");

  music.src="minmhamin.mp3";
  music.play();
}

function sendEmail(){
  window.location.href="mailto:?subject=For you 🌸&body=If I could, I’d give these to you in person… but for now, imagine I’m there 😌";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
